node.text:
Imagine a problem, a concern, or hurdle you currently have in your life.  That problem concern or hurdle is equal to your current level of awareness (consciousness) as it relates to that problem.  When we know how to expand our feeling inside our body, our inspiration, our joy, we can then become more expansive than the level of consciousness we were holding when we perceived the issue as a problem, concern, or hurdle in our lives. This doesn’t mean we don’t need to address the issue, but when we expand our level of awareness all of a sudden what we once perceived as a problem is now a simple pebble in the middle of the road we simply need to step over. 

Follow @DavidSamuelStraus  for more daily wisdom!

What is your takeaway from this video? Share it with me in the comments below!👇

node.title: How to solve a problem with @DavidSamuelStraus 🧐

node.text:
Your language to the universe is frequency! The word consciousness is thrown about so casually that it’s easy to lose sight of what it means, even more so when it is defined as being “awakened.” Awakened consciousness is a state of being aware that you are aware. It is a realization that you are the watcher, the witness within you—not the analyzer, not the thinker, not even the meditator, but that which is the impartial witness of every aspect of your being and doing. 

Follow @MichaelbBeckwith for more!

node.title: Follow @MichaelbBeckwith for more wisdom on the law of attraction!✨

node.text: Tips on Advancing Your Career

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on September 06, 2021. May be an image of ‎text that says '‎Tips on Advancing Your Career ۔uce: via the Muse THE SONO‎'‎.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on September 06, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1. Every year or two, spend some time really thinking about your career. Go out and warm up your network, check out new opportunities, and do some salary comparisons. You make smarter career decisions when you have real data. Also, if you are afraid or uncomfortable, you are probably onto something awesome! Fear means you are growing your comfort zone. -Christie Mims, Career Coach THE GOOD'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on September 06, 2021. May be an image of text that says '2. Don't be afraid to speak up in a meeting or to schedule a sit down with a colleague or boss -whether to hash out details on a project or deal with a sensitive situation. When it comes to having your ideas heard, or to really connecting with co-workers, never underestimate the power of face time and the importance of in-person communication. -Catherine Straut, Assistant Editor of Elle THE'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on September 06, 2021. May be an image of text that says '3. Some people think the office is the place to be all power, all brilliance, all the time. And while you should strive to make a powerful and brilliant impression, an occasional question or clarification won't discount your abilities-but it may help you squeeze through a tricky situation with your reputation intact. -Sara McCord, Staff Writer and Editor at The Muse'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on September 06, 2021. May be an image of text that says '4. Take criticism or "feedback" for what it is: a gift given to you to make you better at what you do. Don't concern yourself with the person or the method of delivery. Instead, glean out the teachable nuggets and move on. -Michelle Bruno, President of Bruno Group Signature Events GOOD SLONO'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on September 06, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5. I know. You've heard it a thousand times: Dress for the job you want, not the one you've got. But I think this message goes far beyond the clothes you wear every day: It's how you present yourself in meetings and at office events, how you interact with staff both above and below you, and how seriously you take your work. -Adrian Granzella Larssen, Editor-in-Chief at The Muse THE GOOD'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on September 06, 2021. May be an image of text that says '6. In chaos, there is opportunity. Most major career accelerations happen when someone steps into a a mess and makes a difference. -Kristi Hedges, Leadership Coach THE GOOD 1O00'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on September 06, 2021. May be an image of text that says '7. Work harder than everyone under you or above you. Nothing commands respect more than a good work ethic. This means being the first one at the event in the morning and the ast one to leave in the evening. No one said this gig was easy. -Keith Johnston, Event Consultant at Plannerwire SONO'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on September 06, 2021. May be an image of ‎text that says '‎8. ۔ng a mentor within your company is particularly valuable- can identify opportunities for advancement you might overlook, guide you through challenging projects, and help you build relationships with higher-ups. Most importantly, if she's influential, she can earn you recommendations for special projects or teams that you might not have been considered for otherwise. And these are the factors that are going to pave the way for success at your company. -Jessica Taylor, Writer GOOO SIONO‎'‎.
